==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ferrous
<hw>Fer"rous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>ferreux</ets>. See <er>Ferreous</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>Pertaining to, or derived from, iron; -- especially used of
compounds of iron in which the iron has its lower valence of two;
<as>as, <ex>ferrous</ex> sulphate</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

